data.name: Term Deposit
data.description: A Westpac Term Deposit lets you invest your money with the certainty of a fixed interest rate and a choice of terms.

features.additionalInfo: Personal Customers can open account either by Branch, Phone or Online.
Statements sent includes confirmation, maturity, renewal and repayment advices
Interest is paid: Monthly, yearly or at Maturity (where the term is 12 months or less) or at the end of any notice period.

eligibility.additionalValue: Those with an Australian residential address and who are currently in Australia.

fees.name: Refunding a Bank cheque no longer required - original presented
Refunding / Replacing a Bank cheque - original lost, stolen or destroyed

depositRates.additionalInfo: Offer available from 8th August 2022 for a limited time only on Term Deposits opened or renewed by Westpac personal and business customers. Available on deposits from $5,000 - $5,000,000 with interest paid monthly. Terms and conditions apply.

depositRates.additionalValue: An additional online bonus rate will be added when you open or renew online. Applies across any rate and term, as well as on our special rate offer for terms mentioned above. Rate applies for a single term. Higher or lower rates may apply for subsequent terms. Rate will not be automatically applied to a renewing Term Deposit.
